  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK925">
<l>kaiyaṟiyāmai yuṭaittē poruḷkoṭuttu</l>
<l>meyyaṟi yāmai koḷal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To give money and purchase unconsciousness is the result of one's ignorance of (one's own actions).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
